00:13:13.190 --> 00:13:15.150
Enainpetdeset milijonov.

239
00:13:17.570 --> 00:13:18.760
To zveni cinično.

240
00:13:18.960 --> 00:13:21.340
Kaj pa, če stranke
izgubite izpred oči?


241
00:13:21.540 --> 00:13:24.190
Stranke?  Katere stranke?
