še vedno prodaja zavarovanje.


293
00:16:19.910 --> 00:16:22.220
Daj no, brez teorij zarote.

294
00:16:22.410 --> 00:16:24.970
Sin moj, oprosti, ampak ti si paranoičen.

295
00:16:25.160 --> 00:16:28.820
Ok, bi mi naredili uslugo?

296
00:16:29.770 --> 00:16:31.730
Bi me nehali klicat "moj sin."

297
00:16:32.320 --> 00:16:35.480
Nisem tvoj sin, Mike.

298
00:16:36.690 --> 00:16:38.270
Pomiri se, prav?

299
00:16:38.900 --> 00:16:41.760
Ali res želite, da vas kot
odvetnika jemljejo resno?


300
00:16:41.960 --> 00:16:44.320
- Bom.
- Dovolj, fantje.


301
00:16:48.110 --> 00:16:49.630
Ali res mislite

302
00:16:49.830 --> 00:16:52.260
G. Loewen me namerava uničiti?

303
00:16:52.460 --> 00:16:55.730
ja  Zakaj bi nas sicer
tako dolgo zavlačeval?


304
00:16:56.480 --> 00:16:58.300
Dovolj je.  Tožil ga bom.

305
00:16:58.500 --> 00:17:01.470
Nikoli nisi nikogar tožil.

306
00:17:01.660 --> 00:17:03.610
To bom naredil.

307
00:17:04.230 --> 00:17:08.070
Misliš, da je pri 75 letih
pravi čas za kaj takega?


308
00:17:08.900 --> 00:17:10.630
Starci ne tožijo.

309
00:17:10.830 --> 00:17:13.800
Če te nekdo poskuša izkoristiti,

310
00:17:14.000 --> 00:17:16.760
in ugotoviš, ni
važno koliko si star.


311
00:17:16.960 --> 00:17:18.670
Hoče, da izstopim iz posla

312
00:17:18.870 --> 00:17:21.770
in tega ne bom dovolil.

